# Post-edit verification

[AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) is the workflow source of truth.

After substantive edits, run **`npm run verify`** (**`vitest run`**, then **`npm run build`**: `tsc -b` + `vite build`) and fix any failures before finishing.

Vitest is configured in [vite.config.ts](vite.config.ts) (`test`); specs live under [tests/](tests/).
